title: The Power Of Association | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Power Of Association | Joel Osteen
description:
Who you choose to associate with can have a powerful impact on your destiny. Get around people who will inspire you to dream bigger. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
